data.description: Welcome home to 104 W. Wareingwood Drive! Historic Dalraida home with modern updates and renovations throughout! Large corner lot with gorgeous landscaping, mature trees and a circular drive. A carport cleverly converted with a garage door and a separate second carport provide plenty of covered parking and an additional parking pad area. As you enter the home, you will appreciate the large family room with beautiful hardwood floors, bay window and a wood burning fireplace. Just beyond the family room is a perfectly sized formal dining room. The dining room joins an amazing kitchen that's been totally renovated and updated with a huge island, tons of designer cabinetry and granite countertops and gas range. Off the kitchen is a sitting room/den perfect for family gatherings. The spacious master bedroom features a cedar walk-in closet. Downstairs are two other guest rooms and a full bath. Down the hallway leading to the large laundry room the walls are lined with built-in cabinetry floor to ceiling and a great tech-center desk area. Upstairs has two nice sized bedrooms and a full bath. You'll love the outdoor living space of this incredible home!  Through a pair of sliding glass doors off the sitting room step out onto a large, covered patio with brick paver courtyard and a huge outdoor fireplace. This home has over 800 square feet of basement space creating the ideal workshop. Additional features: crown molding throughout downstairs, granite and quartz countertops throughout, and a tankless water heater. Schedule today for a private tour.
